summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 25631, entitled: "An ordinance providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of certain portions of Lots Nineteen (19), to Twenty-three (23), inclusive, Block Ninety-six (96), in the Plat of Lake Union Shore Lands, for municipal purposes, and providing that the payment for the same be made from the General Fund", approved the 12th day of November 1910, and published the 15th day of November 1910.
